    "sz_v2_action_text": {
      "scenario_reactions": {
        "action": "Strike back. No hesitation, no warning \u2014 Shake explodes off the bed toward the older man, aiming to close the distance before he reaches the block. Move fast and hard, drive him back into the counter, make him the problem the younger one has to solve. Shake does not know what the thing under his skin is, only that it is already moving with him."
      },
