    "sz_v2_cast1_text": {
      "scenario_reactions": {
        "sz_v2_cast1": "The two men breaking into the apartment. The older one never got to the knife block \u2014 Shake crossed the room and drove him through it, bottles and glass and the drawer front all collapsing at once. The younger one dropped the crowbar. He said nothing. He just looked at Shake like a thing that had gone wrong in a night already full of wrong things, and then he ran."
      },
      "reaction_tags": [
        "kinetic",
        "Tank",
        "spatial",
        "phasing"
      ],
      "skills": {
        "streetwise": 1
      },
      "history": [
        {
          "timestamp": "T+0",
          "description": "Battering Ram (cast_mode) \u2014 lore seed captured",
          "type": "session_zero"
        }
      ]
    },
    "sz_v2_cast1": {
      "history": [
        {
          "timestamp": "T+0",
          "description": "Battering Ram cast_mode: option 2",
          "type": "session_zero"
        }
      ]
    },
    "sz_v2_rider1_text": {
      "scenario_reactions": {
        "sz_v2_rider1": "A wound. The older intruder had powers too \u2014 something that sharpened the edges of what he touched. When Shake drove him into the counter, the man got a hand on him and opened a gash down his left forearm that ran deep enough to see fascia. Shake finished him, then sat on his kitchen floor with a dishrag wrapped around it and stitched himself up by flashlight. It scarred. He still flexes the hand sometimes when he is thinking."
      },
      "reaction_tags": [],
      "skills": {
        "survival": 1
      },
      "history": [
        {
          "timestamp": "T+0",
          "description": "Battering Ram (rider) \u2014 lore seed captured",
          "type": "session_zero"
        }
      ]
    },
    "sz_v2_rider1": {
      "history": [
        {
          "timestamp": "T+0",
          "description": "Battering Ram rider: option 1",
          "type": "session_zero"
        }
      ]
    },
    "sz_v2_cast2_text": {
      "scenario_reactions": {
        "sz_v2_cast2": "Another one like him. Someone becoming prominent in the city after the Onset \u2014 a figure Shake had seen at a distance twice before actually meeting, the way you see someone in a hospital corridor and start filing them before you know their name. Not a friend. Not yet an enemy. Someone whose ability worked in the same register as his own second one, and who moved through a room like the room was negotiable. Watching them was what made Shake notice the quiet thing in himself that had been waiting."
      },
      "reaction_tags": [
        "spatial",
        "phasing",
        "cognitive",
        "Controller"
      ],
      "skills": {
        "instruction": 1
      },
      "history": [
        {
          "timestamp": "T+0",
          "description": "Teleportation (cast_mode) \u2014 lore seed captured",
          "type": "session_zero"
        }
      ]
    },
    "sz_v2_cast2": {
      "history": [
        {
          "timestamp": "T+0",
          "description": "Teleportation cast_mode: option 1",
          "type": "session_zero"
        }
      ]
    },
    "sz_v2_rider2_text": {
      "scenario_reactions": {
        "sz_v2_rider2": "It will not put him inside another object. No splicing. Shake learned this the first time he tried to step to the wrong side of a wall he could not see through \u2014 the ability simply refused, a flat no-go pressure in the back of his skull, the way a hand refuses to close on a hot stove. He can step into space. He cannot step into matter. If the destination is occupied, he does not arrive."
      },
      "reaction_tags": [
        "spatial",
        "translative",
        "phasing"
      ],
      "skills": {
